# ai-housemaker PR Description

> **Canonical workflow:** `ai-housemaker/.cursor/rules/workflow/development-guideline.mdc`

## Scope

Repo: **ai-housemaker** (`Documents/workspaces/ai-housemaker`).

PR **title** and **squash commit**: English — see `pr-conventions.mdc`.

PR **description body**: **Japanese** — section order below.

Full skill: `.agents/skills/ai-housemaker-pr-description/SKILL.md`
Agent prompt: `.github/prompts/create-pr-ai-housemaker.prompt.md`

## Section order (mandatory)

1. `### 概要` — `Before:` / `After:` bullets only (no intro paragraph)
2. Screenshots (optional) — between After and 仕様
3. `仕様：` — acceptance criteria bullets
4. `### 対応内容` — 実装 / 単体テスト / featureテスト / 動作確認 (flat checkboxes)
5. `### レビュワー確認項目` — 動作確認 / コードレビュー (flat checkboxes)
6. `### タスクリンク` — Notion + spec + Figma
7. `### 備考` — tests, diff stats, out-of-scope, follow-ups, rollback

## Draft path

`docs/pr/<type>-<scope>-no<NN>.md` before `gh pr create`.

## Hard rules

- Before = problems; After = outcomes (not file lists).
- No nested bullets under 対応内容 checkboxes.
- Do not mark 動作確認 done if designer QA is pending.
- Verify spec/Figma/Notion links exist before linking.
